uage":"iba","lang_name":"Iban"},{"language":"gil","lang_name":"Gilbertese"},{"language":"sr","lang_name":"Serbian"},{"language":"id","lang_name":"Indonesian"},{"language":"fa-translit","lang_name":"Persian (Latin)"},{"language":"ik","lang_name":"Inupiaq"},{"language":"srn","lang_name":"Sranan Tongo"},{"language":"tpi","lang_name":"Tok Pisin"},{"language":"fa","lang_name":"Persian"},{"language":"sk","lang_name":"Slovak"},{"language":"med","lang_name":"Melpa"},{"language":"bg","lang_name":"Bulgarian"},{"language":"ch","lang_name":"Chamorro"},{"language":"en","lang_name":"English"},{"language":"fj","lang_name":"Fijian"},{"language":"naq","lang_name":"Khoekhoegowab"},{"language":"kn","lang_name":"Kannada"},{"language":"cy","lang_name":"Welsh"},{"language":"ky","lang_name":"Kirghiz"},{"language":"fi","lang_name":"Finnish"}]},{"phelps":"BH11209","text":"## SOTPELA PREA BILONG KOLI LONG OLGETA WAN WAN DE\n* Short Obligatory Prayer\n\n* Wan wan Bahá’í i ken kolim dispela prea wanpela taim long olgeta wan wan de namel long taim bilong belo stret i go inap long taim bilong san i go daun.  Pastaim em i wasim han na pes, na bihain em i sanap na em i tanim pes bilong em i go long Ples Matmat bilong Bahá’u’lláh long Ples Holi (Israel).  Olsem long Papua Niugini em i sanap na em i lukluk i go long ples we san i go daun na em i tanim i go long raithan liklik, na em i kolim dispela prea.\n\nO God bilong mi.  Mi tokaut nau long Yu Yet i bin wokim mi, bai mi inap long save long Yu na lotuim Yu. Nau tasol mi tokaut olsem, mi no gat strong na Yu strong tru.  Na mi tokaut tu olsem, mi rabis pinis na Yu holim olgeta samting.  \n\nI no gat narapela God.  Yu tasol i stap. Yu Save Helpim Long Taim Bilong Bikpela Trabel.  Yu Inap Long Yu Yet.","name":"Short Obligatory Prayer","source":"bahaiprayers.net","version":"7eb42b31-b215-4afd-8634-2b4277540f24","book_cats":{"af":{"cat":"Kort verpligte gebed","cat_order":18,"order_in_cat":1},"am":{"cat":"አጭሩ (Short)","cat_order":30,"order_in_cat":1},"ar